videos.headline: Jones fakes out defenders for option TD
videos.description: On 4th-and-goal, Duke's Daniel Jones fakes out the defense with the option and rushes to the outside for a 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Wilson extends Blue Devils' lead with TD
videos.description: Duke's Shaun Wilson rushes up the middle and leaps for a 1-yard touchdown in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Blake connects with Tears for big gain
videos.description: Northern Illinois' Christian Blake lets a pass fly to Spencer Tears for a 43-yard gain in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Harbison breaks out for TD
videos.description: Northern Illinois' Tre Harbison takes the draw to the outside and rushes for a 25-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Childers finds Wesley for long TD
videos.description: Northern Illinois' Marcus Childers connects with Jauan Wesley on a 67-yard touchdown pass to tie the score.

videos.headline: Jones links up with Rahming for TD
videos.description: Duke's Daniel Jones finds T.J. Rahming over the middle for a 33-yard touchdown reception.

videos.headline: Jones finds Wilson for TD
videos.description: Duke's Daniel Jones finds Shaun Wilson for a 11-yard touchdown late in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Wilson finds opening for long gain
videos.description: Duke's Shaun Wilson rushes to the outside and breaks out for a 31-yard gain.

videos.headline: Johnson forces Duke's 1st turnover
videos.description: Northern Illinois' Jawuan Johnson brings the pressure and forces Duke's Daniel Jones to fumble in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Childers finds Wesley wide open for big gain
videos.description: Northern Illinois' Marcus Childers connects with Jauan Wesley over the middle for a 42-yard gain.

videos.headline: Brown scores Duke's 3rd rushing TD
videos.description: Duke's Brittain Brown takes the handoff up the middle and leaps in for the 7-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Tangelo earns 1st career sack on fourth-down stop
videos.description: Northern Illinois tries going for it on fourth-and-5, but Duke's Derrick Tangelo brings the pressure and sacks Marcus Childers in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: Jones leads Duke against Northern Illinois
videos.description: Duke QB Daniel Jones throws for 252 yards and two touchdowns while rushing for 86 yards and another score as the Blue Devils beat the Huskies 36-14 in the Quick Lane Bowl
